<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Boxer Mitch Green, who has fought heavyweight
champion Mike Tyson in the ring and on the street, was arrested
early Friday in Harlem on charges of driving while intoxicated and
